{"slug":"sirkuler-25-932","reference":"Sirkuler_25_0929","gazette":"Ticaret Bakanlığı, Pan Avrupa-Akdeniz Tercihli Menşe Kuralları Revizyonunun 2026 İtibarıyla Ülke Bazlı Sonuçlarına Dair 19 Aralık 2025 Tarihli Duyurusu","title":"Pan Avrupa-Akdeniz Tercihli Menşe Kuralları Revizyonunun 2026 İtibarıyla Ülke Bazlı Sonuçlarına Dair Duyuru","date":"22 Aralık 2025","bodyHtml":"<p>Ticaret Bakanlığı, Pan Avrupa-Akdeniz Tercihli Menşe Kuralları Revizyonunun 2026 İtibarıyla Ülke Bazlı Sonuçlarına Dair Duyuru yayımlamıştır.</p><div class=\"WordSection1\">\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:6.05pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:17.7pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-10.65pt;mso-list:\r\nl1 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:17.7pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt\">I.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">Giriş<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.15pt\"> </span>—<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.15pt\"> </span>Entegrasyon<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\"> </span>için<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.15pt\"> </span>Tasarlanan<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.25pt\"> </span>Sistemin<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\">\r\n</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">Bölünmesi</span><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:6.95pt\">On yılı aşkın süredir Pan-Avrupa-Akdeniz\r\n(PEM) Tercihli Menşe Kurallarına Dair Bölgesel Konvansiyon; Avrupa ve Akdeniz’e\r\nkıyısı bulunan Kuzey Afrika ve Orta Doğu ülkeleri arasındaki tercihli ticaretin\r\nbel kemiğini oluşturmuştur.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:6.9pt\">Sistem, aynı menşe kuralları\r\nseti, bütünleşik kümülasyon bölgesi ve tek bir işleyiş mantığı üzerine kapsamlı\r\nbir entegrasyon projesi olarak tasarlanmıştır. Ülkemizdeki bir otomotiv yan\r\nsanayi<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>tedarikçisinin<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>Fas’tan<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\">\r\n</span>kablo<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>alması<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>veya<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>Fas’taki<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>bir<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>tekstil<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>üreticisinin<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.75pt\"> </span>İsviçre’ye<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>ihracat\r\nyapması PEM sayesinde ortaya çıkan öngörülebilirlikten yararlanabilmiştir.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:7.05pt;text-indent:0cm\">Ancak\r\n1 Ocak 2026 itibariyle önemli değişiklikler olacaktır.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:6.95pt\">PEM<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.5pt\"> </span>Ortak<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.5pt\"> </span>Komitesinin,<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.35pt\"> </span>12<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.45pt\"> </span>Aralık<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.5pt\"> </span>2024’te<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.4pt\">\r\n</span>aldığı<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.35pt\"> </span>2/2024<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.45pt\"> </span>sayılı<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.45pt\">\r\n</span>Karar<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.5pt\"> </span>ile<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.45pt\"> </span>eski<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.45pt\"> </span>PEM<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.5pt\"> </span>kuralları<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.5pt\">\r\n</span>ile Revize PEM kurallarının eşzamanlı uygulaması 31 Aralık 2025’te sona\r\nermektedir ve ülkemizin çabalarına karşın bu tarihten sonra uzatma için uzlaşı\r\nsağla<u>na</u>mamıştır.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:6.05pt;margin-right:7.0pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:7.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt\">Bazı Akit Tarafların Revize\r\nKonvansiyonun iç onay sürecini tamamlayamaması veya serbest ticaret<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.5pt\"> </span>anlaşmalarının<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.55pt\"> </span>(STA)<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.7pt\"> </span>gerekli<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.6pt\"> </span>dinamik<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.5pt\">\r\n</span>atıf<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.55pt\"> </span>hükmü<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.65pt\"> </span>ile<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.7pt\"> </span>güncellenememiş<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.65pt\"> </span>olması<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.6pt\">\r\n</span>nedeniyle 1 Ocak 2026 itibarıyla PEM bölgesinde artık tek bir menşe\r\nkümülasyon sistemi olmayacak; farklı menşe kümülasyon bölgeleri oluşacaktır:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:43.0pt;text-indent:-17.95pt;mso-list:l1 level2 lfo3;\r\ntab-stops:43.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol;\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Bölge<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\"> </span>R<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\"> </span>—<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span>Revize<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.15pt\"> </span>PEM kurallarını<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.15pt\"> </span>uygulayan<span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt\"> </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">taraflar</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-right:7.2pt;mso-list:l1 level2 lfo3;\r\ntab-stops:43.05pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-font-width:99%\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">Bölge C — 2012 PEM\r\nKonvansiyonu (veya daha eski ikili protokoller) altında kalan taraflar<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.05pt\">Bu durum, tedarik\r\nzincirlerini, kümülasyon imkânlarını, gümrük denetimi risklerini,\r\nfiyatlandırmayı,<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>kurumsal<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>tedarik<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\">\r\n</span>yapılandırmalarını<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>ve<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>ürün<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>tasarım<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>kararlarını<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.75pt\"> </span>etkileyebilecek önemli ve yapısal bir kırılmayı temsil\r\netmektedir.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:22.35pt;text-indent:-15.3pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3;\r\ntab-stops:22.35pt\">II.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->1<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span>Ocak<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span>2026’da<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\">\r\n</span>Ne<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\"> Değişiyor?</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:19.05pt;text-indent:-12.0pt;\r\nmso-list:l2 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:19.05pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span></b><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt\">Paralel<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\"> </span>kural<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span>setlerinin sona<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.05pt\"> </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">ermesi</span><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:7.15pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:7.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">Bilindiği üzere 2025 yılı\r\nPEM bölgesi açısından istisnai bir yıldı: İhracatçılar, ikili düzenlemelere\r\nbağlı olarak eski veya revize PEM kurallarından birini seçebiliyordu. Bu\r\nesneklik<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.25pt\"> </span>artık<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.25pt\"> </span>mümkün<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.25pt\">\r\n</span>olmayacaktır.<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\"> </span><b>2026’dan<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt\">\r\n</span>itibaren<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt\"> </span>her<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.3pt\"> </span>ikili<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt\"> </span>ilişki<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt\"> </span>için<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.3pt\"> </span>tek<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt\"> </span>bir<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.25pt\"> </span>kural<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt\"> </span>seti </b><span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">uygulanabilecektir.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:6.05pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:43.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-17.95pt;mso-list:\r\nl2 level2 lfo2;tab-stops:43.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:\r\n10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-font-width:99%\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">Revize<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt\"> </span>PEM<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span>Kuralları</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">,<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n.05pt\"> </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt\">veya</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:6.9pt;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo2;tab-stops:43.05pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol;\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]-->Aynı menşe kurallarını ifade eden 2012 PEM\r\nKonvansiyonu veya eski ikili <span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">protokoller</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:7.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">Eğer<span style=\"letter-spacing:4.0pt\"> </span>iki<span style=\"letter-spacing:4.0pt\"> </span>ticaret<span style=\"letter-spacing:4.0pt\">\r\n</span>ortağı<span style=\"letter-spacing:4.0pt\"> </span>uyumlu<span style=\"letter-spacing:4.0pt\"> </span>değilse,<span style=\"letter-spacing:4.0pt\">\r\n</span><b>kümülasyon<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n4.0pt\"> </span>otomatik<span style=\"letter-spacing:4.0pt\"> </span>olarak<span style=\"letter-spacing:4.0pt\"> </span>imkânsız<span style=\"letter-spacing:4.0pt\">\r\n</span>hale <span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">gelmektedir</span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:19.05pt;text-indent:-12.0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo2;\r\ntab-stops:19.05pt\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Çapraz<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\"> </span>kümülasyona<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.15pt\"> </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">etkisi</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:7.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">Çapraz<span style=\"letter-spacing:.7pt\"> </span>kümülasyon,<span style=\"letter-spacing:.85pt\"> </span>tedarik<span style=\"letter-spacing:.8pt\"> </span>zincirindeki<span style=\"letter-spacing:.85pt\"> </span>tüm<span style=\"letter-spacing:.9pt\"> </span>ülkelerin<span style=\"letter-spacing:.95pt\"> </span><b>aynı<span style=\"letter-spacing:.85pt\"> </span>PEM<span style=\"letter-spacing:.8pt\"> </span>versiyonunu<span style=\"letter-spacing:.9pt\"> </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">uygulaması&nbsp;</span></b></span><span style=\"text-indent: 0cm; letter-spacing: -0.25pt;\">ve</span><span style=\"text-indent: 0cm;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"text-indent: 0cm; letter-spacing: -0.1pt;\">güncellenmiş</span><span style=\"text-indent: 0cm;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"text-indent: 0cm; letter-spacing: -0.1pt;\">STA’ların</span><span style=\"text-indent: 0cm;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"text-indent: 0cm; letter-spacing: -0.1pt;\">yürürlükte</span><span style=\"text-indent: 0cm;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"text-indent: 0cm; letter-spacing: -0.1pt;\">olması</span><span style=\"text-indent: 0cm;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"text-indent: 0cm; letter-spacing: -0.1pt;\">hâlinde</span><span style=\"text-indent: 0cm;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"text-indent: 0cm; letter-spacing: -0.1pt;\">mümkündür</span><span style=\"text-indent: 0cm; letter-spacing: -0.1pt;\">.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-left: 0cm;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:6.95pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:7.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">Ülkelerin<span style=\"letter-spacing:4.0pt;\r\nmso-font-width:150%\"> </span>durumunu<span style=\"letter-spacing:4.0pt;\r\nmso-font-width:150%\"> </span>gösteren<span style=\"letter-spacing:4.0pt;\r\nmso-font-width:150%\"> </span>güncel<span style=\"letter-spacing:4.0pt;\r\nmso-font-width:150%\"> </span>bilgilere<span style=\"letter-spacing:4.0pt;\r\nmso-font-width:150%\"> </span>aşağıdaki<span style=\"letter-spacing:4.0pt;\r\nmso-font-width:150%\"> </span>linkten<span style=\"letter-spacing:4.0pt;\r\nmso-font-width:150%\"> </span>erişim<span style=\"letter-spacing:4.0pt;\r\nmso-font-width:150%\"> </span>mümkündür: </span><a href=\"https://taxation-customs.ec.europa.eu/customs/international-affairs/pan-euro-mediterranean-cumulation-and-pem-convention_en\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;color:#0462C1;letter-spacing:-.1pt\">https://taxation-customs.ec.europa.eu/customs/international-affairs/pan-euro-</span></b></a><a href=\"https://taxation-customs.ec.europa.eu/customs/international-affairs/pan-euro-mediterranean-cumulation-and-pem-convention_en\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;color:#0462C1;letter-spacing:-.1pt\">mediterranean-cumulation-and-pem-convention_en</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n</div><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:6.05pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:17.7pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-10.65pt;mso-list:\r\nl0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:17.7pt\">\r\n\r\n<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:TR;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\"><br clear=\"all\" style=\"page-break-before:always;mso-break-type:section-break\">\r\n</span></b>\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:3.8pt;margin-right:7.0pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:7.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt\">AB<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.45pt\"> </span>Resmî<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.45pt\"> </span>Gazetesinde<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.6pt\"> </span>yayımlanan<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.45pt\"> </span>son<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.45pt\"> </span>bildirime<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.5pt\"> </span>göre<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.5pt\"> </span>(</span></b><a href=\"https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/PDF/?uri=OJ%3AC_202506212\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;color:#0462C1\">OJ<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.45pt\"> </span>C/2025/6216</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt\">)</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">,<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.45pt\"> </span>aşağıdaki<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.45pt\"> </span>önemli bloklar arasında çapraz kümülasyon artık işlemeyecektir:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top: 6.05pt;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-font-width:99%\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">EFTA<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.1pt\"> </span>↔<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span>Agadir/EuroMed<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>↔<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span>AB<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span>↔<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">Türkiye</span><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" align=\"left\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-font-width:99%\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">CEFTA<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.05pt\"> </span>↔ EFTA ↔ <span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">Türkiye</span><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" align=\"left\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-font-width:99%\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">CEFTA<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.05pt\"> </span>↔ AB ↔ <span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">Türkiye</span><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p style=\"margin-left:27.05pt;text-indent:-20.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3;\r\ntab-stops:27.05pt\">III.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Ülke<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.25pt\"> </span>Sınıflandırması:<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span>Bölge<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\"> </span>R<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\"> </span>ve<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\"> </span>Bölge<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-.5pt\">C</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:7.0pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:7.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">31<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.65pt\"> </span>Aralık<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.65pt\"> </span>2025’e<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.7pt\"> </span>kadar<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.7pt\"> </span>onay<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.65pt\"> </span>süreçleri<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.65pt\"> </span>devam<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.65pt\"> </span>edebileceği<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.65pt\"> </span>için<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.65pt\"> </span>son<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.65pt\"> </span>durum<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.65pt\">\r\n</span>değişebilecek<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.65pt\"> </span>olmakla\r\nbirlikte genel yönelim <b>bölge içinde\r\ngiderek ayrışma yönündedir.<o:p></o:p></b></span></p><p style=\"margin-left:21.7pt;text-indent:-14.65pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:21.7pt\">A.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Avrupa<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.15pt\"> </span>Birliği<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\">\r\n</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt\">(AB)</span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:6.95pt\"><b>Durum: </b>Büyük ölçüde R — AB, STA’larının çoğunda dinamik atıf\r\nsürecini tamamladı. <b>Etkisi:<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.4pt\"> </span></b>Uyumlu<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.4pt\"> </span>ortaklarla<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.45pt\"> </span>kolaylaşma,<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.45pt\"> </span>diğerleriyle<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.45pt\"> </span>ise<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.35pt\"> </span>eski<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.4pt\"> </span>kurallara<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.5pt\">\r\n</span>göre<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.45pt\"> </span>ikili<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.4pt\"> </span>ticaret<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.4pt\">\r\n</span>ve<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.45pt\"> </span>çapraz kümülasyon\r\nimkanlarının önemli derecede zedelenmesi.<o:p></o:p></p><p style=\"margin-top:6.05pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:\r\n21.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-14.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:21.05pt\">B.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->EFTA <span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">Devletleri</span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\">İzlanda,<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.15pt\"> </span>Norveç, İsviçre–Lihtenştayn,<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\"> </span>Faroe<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.15pt\"> </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">Adaları</span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">Durum:</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </b><span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.1pt\">Revize</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"letter-spacing:-.25pt\">PEM</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"letter-spacing:-.25pt\">ile</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt\">büyük</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">ölçüde</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">uyumlu.</span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top: 0cm;\"><b>Risk:<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\"> </span></b>Türkiye,<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span>CEFTA<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\">\r\n</span>ve<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\"> </span>bazı Agadir<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span>ortaklarıyla<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.05pt\"> </span>çapraz<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span>kümülasyon<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span>sona<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">erecektir.</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style=\"margin-left:21.7pt;text-indent:-14.65pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:21.7pt\">C.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Agadir<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\"> </span>/<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span>Euromed<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">Ortakları</span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\">Cezayir,<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\"> </span>Mısır,<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\">\r\n</span>İsrail,<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span>Ürdün,<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\"> </span>Lübnan,<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\">\r\n</span>Fas,<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\"> </span>Filistin,<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span>Suriye,<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">\r\n</span>Tunus,<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">Türkiye</span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-right: 7.05pt;\"><b><span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">Durum:</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </b><span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">Yoğun</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">parçalanma</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">tehlikesi</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">nedeniyle</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">kritik</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"letter-spacing:-.3pt\">ve</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt\">özel</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.2pt\">bir</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">durum. </span>Bazıları (ör. Fas–AB) STA’larını\r\ngüncelledi; diğerleri eski rejimde.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:7.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">Ülkemizin<span style=\"letter-spacing:4.0pt\"> </span>konumu<span style=\"letter-spacing:4.0pt\"> </span>özellikle<span style=\"letter-spacing:4.0pt\"> </span>belirleyici<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n4.0pt\"> </span></span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt\">—<span style=\"letter-spacing:4.0pt\"> </span>AB–EFTA–TR,<span style=\"letter-spacing:4.0pt\"> </span>CEFTA–AB–TR<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n4.0pt\"> </span>gibi<span style=\"letter-spacing:4.0pt\"> </span>ana kümülasyon\r\nkoridorları kesintiye uğruyor.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-left:21.7pt;text-indent:-14.65pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:21.7pt\">D.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->CEFTA<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.15pt\"> </span>ve<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.15pt\"> </span>AB<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span>İstikrar<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.15pt\">\r\n</span>&amp;<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\"> </span>Ortaklık<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">Ülkeleri</span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.15pt\">Arnavutluk, Bosna-Hersek,\r\nKuzey Makedonya, Karadağ, Sırbistan, Kosova, Moldova, Gürcistan, Ukrayna<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.05pt\"><b>Durum: </b>Pek çoğu Revize kuralları benimsedi, ancak STA’lar tamamen\r\ngüncellenmedi. <b>Etkisi: </b>“Kümülasyon\r\nkilitlenmesi” — Eksik uyum, EFTA, Türkiye ve hatta bazı durumlarda AB ile\r\nçapraz kümülasyonu engelliyor.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.2pt;line-height:107%\"><b>1<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>Ocak<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>2026<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>itibarıyla<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span></b>ülkemiz<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.75pt\"> </span>açısından<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>PEM<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>bölgesindeki<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.75pt\"> </span>kümülasyon<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>imkanlarını<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>gösteren tablo ekte sunulmaktadır.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.2pt;line-height:107%\">STA’ların\r\ngüncellenmesi süreci devam etmektedir. Kümülasyon alanına katılan yeni bir ülke\r\noldukça söz konusu tablo da güncellenerek Bakanlığımız resmi internet\r\nsitesinden <span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">duyurulacaktır.</span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:6.05pt;margin-right:7.1pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:7.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\n107%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%\">Türkiye – Avrupa Birliği Gümrük\r\nBirliği </span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%\">kapsamındaki doğrudan ticarette bir değişiklik <span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">olmayacaktır.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:6.05pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:17.7pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-10.65pt;mso-list:\r\nl0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:17.7pt\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:5.95pt;margin-right:7.05pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:7.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:107%\">Türkiye<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>ve<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>AB<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>arasında<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\">\r\n</span>AKÇT<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>ile<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>tarım<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\">\r\n</span>alanları<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>başta<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>olmak<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\">\r\n</span>üzere,<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>Mısır,<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>Fas,<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>Tunus<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>ve<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.75pt\"> </span>Balkan\r\nülkeleri ile gerekli süreçlerin tamamlanması için çalışmalar aralıksız\r\nsürdürülmektedir. İlgili tüm ülkelerde zorunlu yasal süreçlerin devam ediyor\r\nolduğu ve mevzuatların da buna göre değişebildiğinin dikkate alınmasında yarar\r\ngörülmektedir. Gelişmeler düzenli olarak <span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">aktarılacaktır.</span><o:p></o:p></p><p><br></p><p>Kaynak:https://ticaret.gov.tr/duyurular/pan-avrupa-akdeniz-tercihli-mense-kurallari-revizyonunun-2026-itibariyla-ulke-bazli-sonuclarina-dair-duyuru</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>\n                                <a target=\"_blank\" class=\"text-danger\" href=\"\">\n                                    \n                                </a>"}
